data.description: Recently remodeled home in a fabulous location. Easy access to major highways for commuting and being close to the wonderful amenities Fort Worth has to offer. Lots extras with this property including 3 large living areas, large detached 2 car garage and workshop with rear access, tons of front and rear parking, beautiful backyard with large paved patio, shade trees and dog runs. Light and bright kitchen with stainless appliances and granite counters. All the work has been done in the bathrooms as well with neutral, light paint colors, new tub surrounds and fixtures. Tons of space inside for family and friends with an open layout and 2 back doors for easy patio access. This property is waiting for a new owner and their personal touches to make it their own.
